IP/Trademarks Lawyer, 1PQE, Dubai
IP/Trademarks Lawyer, 1PQE, Dubai
Location:  --Dubai
This top tier global law firm is looking for a junior lawyer to join its market leading IP practice in Dubai.
The firm boasts a well-established presence in the region; to which its Dubai office remains the centre point and focus for its IP practice. The team performs a broad range of high value contentious and non-contentious protection, exploitation and enforcement work on an international scale. The team also undertakes corporate support work in conjunction with the firm’s strong offering in this area.
Ideal applicants will have gained strong post-qualification experience in trademarks / IP work following on from a strong training contract with relevant seats and impressive academic record. Although not essential, prior experience in the Middle East and/or relevant language skills certainly represents a distinct advantage.
Offering an attractive salary, scope for development and the opportunity to work in a highly reputable team, early applications are encouraged.
For further details, candidates fulfilling the above criteria are invited to send their CV in complete confidence to
